---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact Backyard Sauna Pro"
  description="Get in touch with the Backyard Sauna Pro team."
  canonical="/contact"
>
  <article class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6">Have a question, a correction, or a product suggestion? We read every message.</p>

    <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4 text-sm">The best way to reach us is by email. We typically reply within 1-2 business days.</p>
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@backyardsaunapro.com"
        class="inline-block bg-stone-900 hover:bg-stone-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors text-sm"
      >
        hello@backyardsaunapro.com
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-sm text-stone-500">
      <p class="mb-2 font-medium text-stone-700">Common questions:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1 ml-4">
        <li>Product corrections or outdated pricing? Please email with a link and we will update it.</li>
        <li>Affiliate or partnership inquiries? Same address.</li>
        <li>Press or media? Email with your outlet and we will get back to you.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
